<item>
            <title>[LU-3402] parallel-scale-nfsv4 test metabench: Permission denied</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3402</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;parallel-scale-nfsv4 test metabench failed as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== parallel-scale-nfsv4 test metabench: metabench ==================================================== 11:31:58 (1369593118)
OPTIONS:
METABENCH=/usr/bin/metabench
clients=client-14vm1,client-14vm2.lab.whamcloud.com 
mbench_NFILES=10000
mbench_THREADS=4
client-14vm1
client-14vm2.lab.whamcloud.com
+ /usr/bin/metabench -w /mnt/lustre/d0.metabench -c 10000 -C -S -k
+ chmod 0777 /mnt/lustre
drwxrwxrwx 5 root root 45056 May 26 11:32 /mnt/lustre
+ su mpiuser sh -c &quot;/usr/lib/openmpi/1.4-gcc/bin/mpirun -mca boot ssh -np 8 -machinefile /tmp/parallel-scale-nfs.machines /usr/bin/metabench -w /mnt/lustre/d0.metabench -c 10000 -C -S -k &quot;
Permission denied.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Maloo report: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/ee447e40-c63b-11e2-ad5d-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/ee447e40-c63b-11e2-ad5d-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The same issue also occurred while running other MPI programs (IOR) on NFSv4 clients.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;br/&gt;
Lustre b2_1 build: &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_1/204&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_1/204&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Distro/Arch: RHEL5.9/i686 (client), RHEL5.9/x86_64 (server)&lt;br/&gt;
</environment>
